{"tid":793824,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打嚟緊會去四國松山?","createTime":"2018-08-25T16:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T06:25:20.000Z","uid":60219,"like":25,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fe7c3e26cb3270c9c923db05a942d04e2986faf1","tid":793824,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:49:20.000Z","msg":"四年前12月我獨遊四國，啱啱廿歲第一次獨遊成日蕩失路<br />\n<br />\n當日由廣島港搭船去到松山，check in咗APA酒店之後夜晚七點左右一個人係條街到搵餐廳但搵極都搵唔到<br />\n<br />\n誤打誤撞下入咗一間餐廳食御好燒，個老闆娘好熱情好和藹，當時我一個口靚仔乜都唔識，又凍又餓之下果一餐特別令人難忘<br />\n<br />\n個老闆娘原來後生果陣去過台灣讀書，識小小國語，當晚好努力咁用佢僅僅識得嘅國語同我傾計，問我旅程如何，問我之後會去邊，我又同佢分享下我所見所聞<br />\n<br />\n臨走果陣，佢送我出門口，微微鞠躬用國語講&quot;一路順風&quot;，果種感覺真係...溫暖到不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n奈何當時on99，無記低間餐廳名，一路以來都好想搵返但都搵唔到<br />\n<br />\n直到呢排又誤打誤撞下搵返間餐廳名，係&quot;お好み焼きいちぜん洋食&quot;，睇咗d相，睇咗日本仔食評話係一個老闆娘獨力營運，應該就係呢間無錯了<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/7oXC3EQPdT32\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2F7oXC3EQPdT32&d=VtFwc5N7gImy1hdKMBpwrJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=fc3e3d3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/7oXC3EQPdT32</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然時隔4年，我唔肯定今日個老闆娘係咪依然係同一個人，亦唔知佢仲記唔記得我<br />\n<br />\n但如果有巴打去松山順路嘅話，希望你哋可以去呢間餐廳，食下個老闆娘親手煮嘅御好燒，同埋幫我向佢問候一聲<br />\n<br />\n幫我同佢講，4年前嘅12月，有一晚有一個識講國語嘅男仔嚟到佢間餐廳，個男仔係由廣島去到松山，然後下一站係高松。時至今日，個男仔依然好懷念佢煮嘅御好燒同埋佢當晚咁周到嘅招呼。個男仔依家已經讀完書做緊嘢，雖然有時會做嘢做到有d迷茫，但依然一切安好，而個男仔亦希望老闆娘亦一切安好，一路順風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ab9d97011b3c9ec614b15bdda0ad9e8934da96","tid":793824,"uid":60219,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:53:17.000Z","msg":"有d詞窮 sor for 1999<br />\n但呢件事一直係我心入面好耐，好驚未來都無機會親自同個老闆娘表達謝意<br />\n希望有去松山順路嘅巴打可以代我轉達謝意，唔好令到呢件事變成一個遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8d90da382d567ae4dde6e086a38a045e491ac8","tid":793824,"uid":65292,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T17:09:04.000Z","msg":"無論個老闆娘記唔記得呢篇文都幾warm"},{"pid":"7d09d7d8b5d204171742e92df2adb24af5bc0b49","tid":793824,"uid":35746,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T22:16:39.000Z","msg":"放心，實唔記得，一日至少一個你d 咁既客，人就係犯賤，永遠只會記得西客"},{"pid":"e69a24549ed49f9fdd4025319b41f999b4f29c66","tid":793824,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T00:57:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"12bcbd491de244477b7cca999a6291e28ef19393","tid":793824,"uid":60219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da8d90da382d567ae4dde6e086a38a045e491ac8","tid":793824,"uid":65292,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T17:09:04.000Z","msg":"無論個老闆娘記唔記得呢篇文都幾warm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T02:30:09.000Z","msg":"當時未有hkexpress去四國嘅機，而且松山好少遊客，就算有都係台灣人為主<br />\n<br />\n果陣佢話好少遊客會嚟，甚至更少見過香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ecb9a810bd44c95164433910b380e21a95d344","tid":793824,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T06:33:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fa2231b7c66b339efab9c509d7546c338eaf08c5","tid":793824,"uid":8435,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T06:43:34.000Z","msg":"你親手寫封信寄俾佢會唔會仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc13f2fcfe073bb8530a677ad4f9d0a3cf6973c","tid":793824,"uid":28944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T06:48:31.000Z","msg":"我下年3月自駕四國呀，有乜可幫到你？"},{"pid":"b946c26cfff33540e1c8b51f2078205548c7c52c","tid":793824,"uid":28944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T06:50:19.000Z","msg":"如果你有合照咪曬一張我可親手交比佢，如果間野仲響道既話"},{"pid":"c17b65317ecacfdd51d7f50cea7f814d444c7ef0","tid":793824,"uid":172017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T06:59:16.000Z","msg":"我下年一月會去四國，幫巴打問候下老闆娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順便去試食下，巴打咁推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397e376624c563aa070d1e6c82415661ce4235ea","tid":793824,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa2231b7c66b339efab9c509d7546c338eaf08c5","tid":793824,"uid":8435,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T06:43:34.000Z","msg":"你親手寫封信寄俾佢會唔會仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T10:12:34.000Z","msg":"我諗住會啊，不過要先諗下封信點寫同埋點譯做日文先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ac3d6fe7c4fa483752d1e1fb1e4555124c969d","tid":793824,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b946c26cfff33540e1c8b51f2078205548c7c52c","tid":793824,"uid":28944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T06:50:19.000Z","msg":"如果你有合照咪曬一張我可親手交比佢，如果間野仲響道既話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T10:15:58.000Z","msg":"果晚返酒店先諗緊如果有影張合照懷念就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當時個人慌慌張張食完就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實巴打順路嘅話去食下支持下就好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同老闆娘有機會吹水㗎話，同佢講下當時有個香港後生仔嘅第一次獨遊之旅好感激有佢招呼過，希望佢仲記得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d05ec80cfb750e3013f0eb52972e5b4c5e3e55","tid":793824,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c17b65317ecacfdd51d7f50cea7f814d444c7ef0","tid":793824,"uid":172017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T06:59:16.000Z","msg":"我下年一月會去四國，幫巴打問候下老闆娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順便去試食下，巴打咁推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T10:17:13.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望個老闆娘依然仲係到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d938c92f0f71d7a1f39a41ef6e10ce1d0fe1825","tid":793824,"uid":172017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23d05ec80cfb750e3013f0eb52972e5b4c5e3e55","tid":793824,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c17b65317ecacfdd51d7f50cea7f814d444c7ef0","tid":793824,"uid":172017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T06:59:16.000Z","msg":"我下年一月會去四國，幫巴打問候下老闆娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順便去試食下，巴打咁推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T10:17:13.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望個老闆娘依然仲係到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T11:00:20.000Z","msg":"唔好咁講啦，我呢次都係獨遊，都想試多啲唔同既野<br />\n去認識下本地人同人傾下偈都係一種唔錯既體驗<br />\n雖然有時真係雞同鴨講咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54af3e07319637883f1eae6390136f5b51185937","tid":793824,"uid":3932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T11:02:14.000Z","msg":"去日本好易啫<br />\n樓主不如快啲揾個假期親自去探下老闆娘"},{"pid":"be4a8d2eefcda4cf5f6d50e12973480db8f83c06","tid":793824,"uid":33727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T11:27:51.000Z","msg":"樓主都幾勁, 第一次獨遊就去四國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f2a6cb4efec398067c4eacc668a21b3c541848","tid":793824,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d938c92f0f71d7a1f39a41ef6e10ce1d0fe1825","tid":793824,"uid":172017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23d05ec80cfb750e3013f0eb52972e5b4c5e3e55","tid":793824,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c17b65317ecacfdd51d7f50cea7f814d444c7ef0","tid":793824,"uid":172017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T06:59:16.000Z","msg":"我下年一月會去四國，幫巴打問候下老闆娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順便去試食下，巴打咁推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T10:17:13.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望個老闆娘依然仲係到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T11:00:20.000Z","msg":"唔好咁講啦，我呢次都係獨遊，都想試多啲唔同既野<br />\n去認識下本地人同人傾下偈都係一種唔錯既體驗<br />\n雖然有時真係雞同鴨講咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:33:27.000Z","msg":"四國松山果頭應該相對上少d遊客，本地情懷應該濃d，我以前去得好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n松山城同埋大洲城附近有個湖仔都幾靚，順路可以去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26e91c1d8ca86929a9d0f27bf077abdee47c43a","tid":793824,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54af3e07319637883f1eae6390136f5b51185937","tid":793824,"uid":3932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T11:02:14.000Z","msg":"去日本好易啫<br />\n樓主不如快啲揾個假期親自去探下老闆娘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:34:42.000Z","msg":"希望到時佢未執啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5405d9a604588c413004ced81e9e1aca14567f","tid":793824,"uid":60219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be4a8d2eefcda4cf5f6d50e12973480db8f83c06","tid":793824,"uid":33727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T11:27:51.000Z","msg":"樓主都幾勁, 第一次獨遊就去四國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:36:14.000Z","msg":"與其話四國，其實係圍住瀬戶內海為主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時係關西落機搭新幹線去廣島，之後搭船去松山，再之後就JR去高松同德島，最後返關西走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb92bd1b1e7cde29238065fbc183cce6e3d213bf","tid":793824,"uid":87852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T01:28:04.000Z","msg":"聽日會飛高松之後去松山<br />\n幫你問候下老闆娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7661fe2efbbd31c9cf26106793e73891ee3c03e","tid":793824,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb92bd1b1e7cde29238065fbc183cce6e3d213bf","tid":793824,"uid":87852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T01:28:04.000Z","msg":"聽日會飛高松之後去松山<br />\n幫你問候下老闆娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:45:55.000Z","msg":"正啊喂多謝巴打咁有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果佢唔記得我都唔緊要，最緊要知道佢依然一切安好就好好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c5f2dceffb56dfeda689f87acce24089d78204","tid":793824,"uid":85965,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:57:09.000Z","msg":"巴打咁掛住人飛去探佢囉<br />\n隨時做埋間鋪男主人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6f9e3a90df6bf810535c228117214c8823b8ca","tid":793824,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:25:30.000Z","msg":"11月會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54563a9046317390e316f89ae16f72abad1da9c2","tid":793824,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb92bd1b1e7cde29238065fbc183cce6e3d213bf","tid":793824,"uid":87852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T01:28:04.000Z","msg":"聽日會飛高松之後去松山<br />\n幫你問候下老闆娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T17:40:04.000Z","msg":"咁快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我9月頭去 可能照去個間食下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" 